{"openapi":"3.1.0","info":{"title":"Pricing Pipeline API","description":"API (Application Programming Interface) for the partner-store pricing ingestion + analysis system.","contact":{"name":"huizhongwu"},"version":"0.1.0"},"paths":{"/health":{"get":{"tags":["meta"],"summary":"Liveness probe","operationId":"health_health_get","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}}}}},"/harmonise-product":{"get":{"tags":["harmonise"],"summary":"Harmonise a raw product name to canonical model(s)","description":"Returns up to **k** ranked candidate matches for a partner-supplied product name. Each candidate has a 0-1 score, a confidence bucket (HIGH / MEDIUM / LOW / MANUAL) and a per-signal breakdown for explainability.","operationId":"harmonise_product_harmonise_product_get","parameters":[{"name":"q","in":"query","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","minLength":1,"description":"Raw product name to harmonise","title":"Q"},"description":"Raw product name to harmonise"},{"name":"k","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"integer","maximum":20,"minimum":1,"description":"Number of candidates to return","default":5,"title":"K"},"description":"Number of candidates to return"},{"name":"min_confidence","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/Confidence","description":"Minimum confidence bucket","default":"LOW"},"description":"Minimum confidence bucket"}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HarmoniseResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/load-data":{"post":{"tags":["ingest"],"summary":"Submit a CSV (Comma-Separated Values) batch and run the full ingest pipeline","description":"Accepts a multipart upload and runs the eight-step ingest pipeline in-process:\n\n  1. Parse CSV into `stg_price_offer`\n  2. Run INGEST-stage Data Quality rules (parse / format / required-field)\n  3. Harmonise raw product names against the canonical registry\n  4. Run PRE_FACT-stage Data Quality rules (HIGH-severity gate); failing rows are flagged in `dq_bad_records` and do NOT enter fact tables\n  5. Insert change events into `fact_price_offer` + payment child (only PRE_FACT-passing rows)\n  6. Run SEMANTIC-stage Data Quality rules on fact rows (soft signals; failures stay in fact and are flagged for review)\n  7. Update Slowly Changing Dimension Type 2 history\n  8. Write per-batch summary to `dws_partner_dq_per_batch`\n\nReturns `HTTP 202 Accepted` with a `job_id`. At sample-data scale (~4 000 rows) processing completes in seconds, so the response status is `COMPLETED` on return. The full async-queue + parallel-worker + AWS S3 (Amazon Simple Storage Service) staging path for million-row scale is the production design (see `task_c_answers.md` C.3).","operationId":"load_data_load_data_post","requestBody":{"content":{"multipart/form-data":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/Body_load_data_load_data_post"}}},"required":true},"responses":{"202":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/LoadDataAcceptedResponse"}}}},"400":{"description":"Bad Request","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/load-data/{job_id}":{"get":{"tags":["ingest"],"summary":"Poll the progress / status of a load job","operationId":"get_load_job_load_data__job_id__get","parameters":[{"name":"job_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","format":"uuid","description":"The job_id returned by POST /load-data","title":"Job Id"},"description":"The job_id returned by POST /load-data"}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/LoadJobStatus"}}}},"404":{"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"}}},"description":"Not Found"},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/compute-dq":{"post":{"tags":["data-quality"],"summary":"Run Data Quality (DQ) rules against an ingestion batch","description":"Executes all active rules in `dq_rule_catalog` against the specified batch. Aggregates per-rule pass rates into `dq_output` and per-record violations into `dq_bad_records`.\n\nOptionally restrict to specific `rules` and/or `stages` (INGEST / PRE_FACT / SEMANTIC).","operationId":"compute_dq_compute_dq_post","requestBody":{"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ComputeDQRequest"}}},"required":true},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ComputeDQResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/detect-anomalies":{"post":{"tags":["anomaly-detection"],"summary":"Detect pricing anomalies","description":"Runs the four-signal detector (STATISTICAL / TEMPORAL / CROSS_PARTNER / SKU_VARIANCE) over the specified scope.\n\nEach row in the response represents a single triggered signal — an offer that trips multiple signals appears as multiple anomaly entries, each routable to the appropriate team (see `fact_anomaly` in schema.sql).\n\nAll thresholds are read from `dim_anomaly_threshold` and frozen into the response context for replay/audit.","operationId":"detect_anomalies_detect_anomalies_post","requestBody":{"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/DetectAnomaliesRequest"}}},"required":true},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/DetectAnomaliesResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/bad-records":{"get":{"tags":["business-review"],"summary":"List records flagged by Data Quality rules","description":"Powers the business-user review UI. Default filter: `status=NEW` to surface unresolved items. Pagination via `page` / `page_size`.","operationId":"list_bad_records_bad_records_get","parameters":[{"name":"status","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/BadRecordStatus","default":"NEW"}},{"name":"severity","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/Severity"}},{"name":"assignee","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"string","title":"Assignee"}},{"name":"page","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"integer","minimum":1,"default":1,"title":"Page"}},{"name":"page_size","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"integer","maximum":500,"minimum":1,"default":50,"title":"Page Size"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/BadRecordList"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/bad-records/{bad_record_id}/resolve":{"post":{"tags":["business-review"],"summary":"Mark a bad record as resolved (or ignored)","description":"Triggers the business-correction loop. When `replay_batch=true`, the associated `source_batch_id` is re-ingested with the updated abbreviation dictionary / rules — only that batch is re-processed.","operationId":"resolve_bad_record_bad_records__bad_record_id__resolve_post","parameters":[{"name":"bad_record_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"integer","title":"Bad Record Id"}}],"requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ResolveBadRecordRequest"}}}},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ResolveBadRecordResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}}},"components":{"schemas":{"AnomaliesBySeverity":{"properties":{"HIGH":{"type":"integer","title":"High","default":0},"MEDIUM":{"type":"integer","title":"Medium","default":0},"LOW":{"type":"integer","title":"Low","default":0}},"type":"object","title":"AnomaliesBySeverity"},"Anomaly":{"properties":{"anomaly_id":{"type":"integer","title":"Anomaly Id"},"offer_id":{"type":"integer","title":"Offer Id"},"anomaly_type":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/AnomalyType"},"severity":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/Severity"},"signal_score":{"type":"number","maximum":1.0,"minimum":0.0,"title":"Signal Score"},"product_model_id":{"type":"integer","title":"Product Model Id"},"product_model_name":{"type":"string","title":"Product Model Name"},"partner_code":{"type":"string","title":"Partner Code"},"country_code":{"type":"string","title":"Country Code"},"observed_price_usd":{"type":"number","title":"Observed Price Usd"},"explanation":{"type":"string","title":"Explanation"},"context":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/AnomalyContext"},"visualization":{"anyOf":[{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/AnomalyVisualization"},{"type":"null"}]},"detected_at":{"type":"string","format":"date-time","title":"Detected At"}},"type":"object","required":["anomaly_id","offer_id","anomaly_type","severity","signal_score","product_model_id","product_model_name","partner_code","country_code","observed_price_usd","explanation","context","detected_at"],"title":"Anomaly"},"AnomalyContext":{"properties":{"lifecycle_status":{"type":"string","title":"Lifecycle Status"},"lifecycle_factor":{"type":"number","title":"Lifecycle Factor"},"event_suppression_factor":{"type":"number","title":"Event Suppression Factor","default":1.0},"suppression_applied":{"type":"boolean","title":"Suppression Applied","default":false},"suppression_event_id":{"anyOf":[{"type":"integer"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"Suppression Event Id"},"baseline_snapshot":{"anyOf":[{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/BaselineSnapshot"},{"type":"null"}]}},"type":"object","required":["lifecycle_status","lifecycle_factor"],"title":"AnomalyContext"},"AnomalyType":{"type":"string","enum":["STATISTICAL","TEMPORAL","CROSS_PARTNER","SKU_VARIANCE"],"title":"AnomalyType","description":"Designed signal taxonomy. Current implementation only emits `STATISTICAL`\n(compares observed price against the 30-day rolling mean from\n`fact_partner_price_history`). The other three are scoped as future work;\n`fact_anomaly` already has columns to hold their results."},"AnomalyVisualization":{"properties":{"type":{"type":"string","title":"Type","default":"time_series_with_band"},"series":{"items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/TimeSeriesPoint"},"type":"array","title":"Series"},"baseline_band":{"anyOf":[{"additionalProperties":{"type":"number"},"type":"object"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"Baseline Band"},"cross_partner_comparison":{"anyOf":[{"additionalProperties":{"type":"number"},"type":"object"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"Cross Partner Comparison"}},"type":"object","required":["series"],"title":"AnomalyVisualization","description":"Structured payload for frontend chart libraries (Chart.js / Recharts)."},"BadRecordEntry":{"properties":{"bad_record_id":{"type":"integer","title":"Bad Record Id"},"source_batch_id":{"type":"string","format":"uuid","title":"Source Batch Id"},"rule_id":{"type":"string","title":"Rule Id"},"failed_field":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"Failed Field"},"error_message":{"type":"string","title":"Error Message"},"severity":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/Severity"},"status":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/BadRecordStatus"},"assignee":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"Assignee"},"raw_payload":{"additionalProperties":true,"type":"object","title":"Raw Payload"},"detected_at":{"type":"string","format":"date-time","title":"Detected At"},"resolved_at":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string","format":"date-time"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"Resolved At"}},"type":"object","required":["bad_record_id","source_batch_id","rule_id","failed_field","error_message","severity","status","raw_payload","detected_at"],"title":"BadRecordEntry"},"BadRecordList":{"properties":{"total":{"type":"integer","title":"Total"},"page":{"type":"integer","title":"Page"},"page_size":{"type":"integer","title":"Page Size"},"items":{"items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/BadRecordEntry"},"type":"array","title":"Items"}},"type":"object","required":["total","page","page_size","items"],"title":"BadRecordList"},"BadRecordStatus":{"type":"string","enum":["NEW","IN_REVIEW","RESOLVED","IGNORED"],"title":"BadRecordStatus"},"BaselineSnapshot":{"properties":{"window_days":{"type":"integer","title":"Window Days"},"sample_size":{"type":"integer","title":"Sample Size"},"mean":{"type":"number","title":"Mean"},"stddev":{"anyOf":[{"type":"number"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"Stddev"},"p05":{"anyOf":[{"type":"number"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"P05"},"p50":{"anyOf":[{"type":"number"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"P50"},"p95":{"anyOf":[{"type":"number"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"P95"}},"type":"object","required":["window_days","sample_size","mean"],"title":"BaselineSnapshot","description":"Frozen snapshot of dws_product_price_baseline_1d at detection time."},"Body_load_data_load_data_post":{"properties":{"file":{"type":"string","format":"binary","title":"File","description":"CSV file"},"partner_code":{"type":"string","title":"Partner Code","description":"Partner identifier registered in dim_partner"}},"type":"object","required":["file","partner_code"],"title":"Body_load_data_load_data_post"},"ComputeDQRequest":{"properties":{"source_batch_id":{"type":"string","format":"uuid","title":"Source Batch Id","description"